Package: bewitch
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: smartmontools
Suggests: intel-gpu-tools
Description: Server monitoring daemon with TUI
 Bewitch is a lightweight server monitoring tool that collects system metrics
 (CPU, memory, disk, network, temperature, power, GPU, processes) and stores
 them in DuckDB. It includes a terminal UI for real-time monitoring and
 historical analysis, plus an alerting system with webhook support.
 .
 Optional packages: intel-gpu-tools enables Intel iGPU monitoring via
 intel_gpu_top. NVIDIA GPU monitoring requires nvidia-smi from the
 distribution's NVIDIA driver package.
